high_descs: Turn around and go to the desk.
Grab the disk off of the desk.
Turn around and walk to the far wall, turn left and face the safe.
Put the disk in the safe.
Close the safe and turn around and go back to the desk.
Pick up the second disk off of the desk.

Open the safe, put the second disk in, then close the safe.

Turn right and move across the room. Turn left towards the safe in the corner.
Put the CD in the safe.
Turn left and move back to the front of the desk.
Pick up the CD that's laying on top of the desk.
Head back to the safe.
Put the CD in the safe.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table.
Pick up the CD on the right.
Turn right, go straight, turn left, go straight to the white safe and open the door.
Place the CD inside the safe and close the door.

Pick up the remaining CD.
Turn right, go straight, turn left, go straight to the white safe and open the door.
Place the CD inside the safe and close the door.
